          href="https://www.wowhead.com/ptr-2/item=207165/bandolier-of-twisted-blades?bonus=6652:8783:8784:9599:9600:10244:10245&class=4&ilvl=489&spec=260"
        /> | <WH
          text="Талисман Ми'даса"
